HEADWORD: Uneath
<hw>Un*eath"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>une⟦aacute⟧<?/e</ets>; <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>e⟦aacute⟧<?/<?/</ets> easily, easy; akin to OS. <ets><?/<?/i</ets>
