==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Uneath
<hw>Un*eath"</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Not easily; hardly;
scarcely.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Uneath</qex> may she endure the flinty streets.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unedge</ent>⟦br⟧
